{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01JH3UACN94h3QgzonuReomx","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the problem. The key log line is:\n```\nfailed to start gossip client to crdb-cluster-0.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local:26257: initial connection heartbeat failed: grpc: connection error: desc = \"transport: authentication handshake failed: tls: first record does not look like a TLS handshake\" [code 14/Unavailable]\n```\n\ncrdb-cluster-2 is now running in TLS mode, but crdb-cluster-0 and crdb-cluster-1 are still in insecure mode. \n\nThe issue is that crdb-cluster-2 is trying to establish TLS connections to nodes that are still running unencrypted, which causes the handshake to fail. A rolling update won't work here because you can't have mixed secure and insecure nodes communicating in the same cluster. I need to restart all the pods at once so they all transition to TLS mode simultaneously, rather than updating them one at a time.\n\nThe straightforward approach would be to delete all three pods at once, but there's a catch: the StatefulSet is still in the middle of a rolling update, so when the pods restart, crdb-cluster-0 and crdb-cluster-1 would come back up with the old insecure template since they haven't been updated yet. I need to think through the update strategy more carefully to avoid this. If I switch to OnDelete strategy, the rolling update stops and I can delete all three pods simultaneously so they restart with the new TLS template. Since the StatefulSet now has the updated pod template, all pods will come back up in TLS mode and can form a cluster together.\n\nThe data on the PVCs will persist through the restart, and CockroachDB supports transitioning from insecure to secure mode as long as all nodes restart with valid certificates and trust the CA. So the plan is to change the update strategy and delete the pods.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":11556,"cache_read_input_tokens":38843,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":11556},"output_tokens":36,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d7a97e95-9f7d-43e2-8d1d-4df42241feb7","uuid":"9d004304-cb54-474f-84ce-98db66b6b36e","request_id":"req_011CcMQUTTgnVfaqWU9wUut2"}
